---
title: Mediterranean Pesto Chicken Strips with Roast Veggie Couscous & Crumbly Cheese
description: Quickly-cooked chicken strips meld together wonderfully with nutty basil pesto in this Mediterranean-style dish. Make it a meal with fluffy
couscous and crumbly cheese, and now you’ve got yourself a fusion of textures and flavours you simply can’t miss out on!
